ent-AU14CMBCIUapparelvendor = CMB CIU apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Crisis Intervention Unit apparel from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14CMBCIUequipmentvendor = CMB CIU equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Crisis Intervention Unit equipment from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14CMBCIUTacticalMedicVendor = CMB CIU Tactical Medic Vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of Crisis Intervention Unit trauma supplies from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14CMBCIUPilotVendor = CMB CIU aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Crisis Intervention Unit aircrew flight and support gear from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14CMBCIUCommandVendor = CMB CIU command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Crisis Intervention Unit leadership equipment from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14CMBCIUGunnerVendor = CMB CIU automatic rifleman equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Crisis Intervention Unit light-machine gun equipment from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Standard issue for designated LMG crews on naval vessels and outposts. Built to bring fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14CMBCIUSectionLeader = CMB CIU section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Crisis Intervention Unit section-leadership equipment from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14CMBCIUWeaponsVendor = CMB CIU weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Crisis Intervention Unit weaponry from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14CMBCIUSpecialWeaponsVendor = CMB CIU Special Weapons Rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Crisis Intervention Unit heavy and breaching ordnance from the Colonial Marshall Bureau. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14MilitaryPolicemanGenericVendorCIU = CMB CIU internal affairs equipment rack
    .desc = An automated rack hooked up to a small storage of military police equipment.
ent-AU14CMBCIURequisitionVendor = CMB CIU automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
